<br>
If we are to get the spell, unlikely due to spawn time or others camping it, I would sell the spell within 1 week and either give the money to you personally or your guild leader for distribution.  Based on this bid it would be about 200pp each for a party of 18.<br>
<br>
How do people feel about this?<br>
